m_SmtpHost.Name: SMTP Host
m_SmtpHost.Description: The IP address of the server that forwards email at your site

m_SmtpPort.Name: SMTP Port
m_SmtpPort.Description: The TCP port number used to communicate with the email server at your site

m_SenderName.Name: Sender Name
m_SenderName.Description: The text to be shown on email messages as the name of the sender

m_SenderEmailAddress.Name: Sender Email Address
m_SenderEmailAddress.Description: The text to be shown on email messages as the email address of the sender

m_TestEmailSubject.Name: Test Email Subject
m_TestEmailSubject.Description: The subject text that will be used when sending test messages

m_TestEmailMessage.Name: Test Email Message
m_TestEmailMessage.Description: The message text that will be used when sending test messages
